# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [2.5.4] - 2021-12-01 (Latest)
### Fixed
- Calculation result after save (was not updated in group view)

### Added
- Log messages

### Changed
- Classes packages to domain-oriented packages
- Cleanup code (improve code quality)
- Refactor events and separate events
- Refactor settings
- Refactor device errors
- Log information and details

## [2.5.3] - 2021-08-17
### Fixed
- Calibration data request (displayed in service)

### Changed
- View software refactoring (little changes in view display)

## [2.5.2] - 2021-07-14
### Fixed
- Missing i18n resource for calibration dialog

## [2.5.1] - 2021-06-17
### Fixed
- Group logger bugfix (old group logs got log entries from newer groups)
- Group logger state fix
- Group timer (heat/purge) reset bugfix (when added time manually with +5:00 and it was over the maximum value, the time was reset to the maximum value when opening the group settings)
- Wi-fi interface connection fix on foreign os languages
- Device timer crash (114 minutes limit)

## [2.5.0] - 2021-05-25
### Added
- Log mover to usb
- Updater

### Fixed
- Installer autostart bugfix

## [2.4.0] - 2020-10-30
### Added
- Group/room chart
